  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.2">
<l>mēṟṟōṉṟip pūkkāḷ mēlula kaṅkaḷiṉ mītupōy</l>
<l>mēṟṟōṉṟum cōti vēta mutalvar valaṅkaiyil</l>
<l>mēṟṟōṉṟu māḻiyiṉ veñcuṭar pōlac cuṭātemmai</l>
<l>māṟṟōlaip paṭṭavar kūṭṭattu vaittukoḷ kiṟṟirē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O flowers that appear above! Will you be able to place us</l>
<l>in the crowd of people who have shifted to a group other than [God’s],</l>
<l>not burning [me] like the cruel fire of the discus on the right hand</l>
<l>of God [praised in] the Vedas from [the land of] the Light</l>
<l rend="indent">that appears above,</l>
<l>having gone beyond the upper worlds!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
